OL,7,FA third of buyers have experienced a
OL,8,Fscam on popular second-hand
OL,9,Fmarketplaces in the last two years, a
OL,10,Fsurvey suggests.
OL,12,FWhich? warned that fraud is "soaring"
OL,13,Fon second-hand marketplaces after
OL,14,Ffinding that 32% of buyers and 22% of
OL,15,Fsellers had experienced a scam when
OL,16,Fusing them.
