OL,5,Cyears'
OL,7,FSome 76,946 cases were reported and
OL,8,F#40.9 million lost to these scams in
OL,9,Fthe first half of 2023.
OL,11,FConsumers are advised to be cautious
OL,12,Fwhen shopping on second-hand
OL,13,Fplatforms, and to check the seller's
OL,14,Freviews and profile.
