OL,3,CThird of buyers 'experienced scam on
OL,4,Csecond-hand marketplaces in last two
OL,5,Cyears'
OL,7,FWhich? director of policy and advocacy
OL,8,FRocio Concha said: "Second-hand
OL,9,Fmarketplaces can be a great way to
OL,10,Fsave money and shop in a more
OL,11,Fsustainable way so it's worrying that
OL,12,Fa third of buyers have experienced a
OL,13,Fscam in the last two years.
OL,15,F"When buying and selling second-hand
OL,16,Fgoods online, it's important that
OL,17,Fpeople properly check the seller's
OL,18,Freviews and profile ` especially if
OL,19,Fthey are on the hunt for expensive
OL,20,Fgoods.
