OL,5,Cyears'
OL,7,F"However, the responsibility should
OL,8,Fnot fall wholly on consumers to
OL,9,Fprotect themselves from scammers.
OL,10,FSecond-hand marketplaces need to
OL,11,Fensure there are proper checks in
OL,12,Fplace to prevent scammers from
OL,13,Fadvertising in the first place and
OL,14,Fthat any scam profiles are quickly
OL,15,Fremoved."
